{"tid":252272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劏豬凳吳得掂坐果班機爆玻璃折返香港","createTime":"2017-05-21T14:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T02:15:52.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a1f1b51aa788b7fc67ba596f5dda3decaa76659","tid":252272,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.flightradar24.com/data/flights/cx253#d756649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flightradar24.com%2Fdata%2Fflights%2Fcx253%23d756649&d=omBmzASQdSWdcKXRX4O2Nk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a65c3734\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.flightradar24.com/data/flights/cx253#d756649</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170521/56724389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170521%2F56724389&d=omBmzASQdSWdcKXRX4O2Nk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=452da75e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170521%2F56724389&h=9c91f049\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170521/56724389</a><br />\n<br />\n 教育局局長吳克儉今日下午原定乘搭國泰航機CX253前往英國倫敦，出席由英國文化協會舉辦的全球國際教育論壇並發表演說。據悉該班航機因故障需折返香港國際機場，教育局局長新聞秘書接受《蘋果》查詢時指，根據局長行程確實是乘搭該航班到英國，現正查詢局長有否受傷。<br />\n<br />\n機管局回覆查詢，指今晚8時許，機管局收到控制塔通知，指一班飛往倫敦的國泰航班CX253需要折返及局部戒備，航班於晚上8時45分安全降落香港國際機場，機場運作不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空回應指，今日下午2時39分由香港出發前往倫敦希思羅機場的CX253航班，由於發現機長前方擋風玻璃出現裂痕，故按既定預防措施折返香港。國泰指一向以乘客及機組人員的安全為首要考慮，該班載有270名乘客的波音777-300ER客機於晚上8時46分安全降落香港國際機場，在等候期間已為乘客於候機大堂安排膳食，並調配另一客機和機組人員再次啟程，預計該航班將於5月22日凌晨1時出發。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在香港航空討論區fb群組上載多張疑為該客機降落在本港機場圖片，照片可見前方擋風玻璃出現裂痕。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長吳克儉周日起一連5日將前往英國倫敦，出席由英國文化協會舉辦的全球國際教育論壇「Going Global 2017」並發表演說。論壇今年主題是「國際城市：連繫人才，推動改變」，各地教育界領袖將討論持續和高等教育的未來。吳克儉亦將在分組討論環節，與英國和聯合國教育、科學及文化組織專家以「2050年城市：為不確定的未來建構技能」發表演說，並與各地教育官員舉行雙邊會議。　"},{"pid":"d674b432a5a7003e9e8f03ab93154f5a996ed1e4","tid":252272,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:55:07.000Z","msg":"天意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ef5dd754e655653b1fb35cf302e19ff708b53a","tid":252272,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676811b20d26ecff76ef2089a85a06b180a859c6","tid":252272,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:08:34.000Z","msg":"等睇聽日東方頭版"},{"pid":"cb9658bea6dbf667ecc3ad8913aa67211b05d96d","tid":252272,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"國泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f0e83a859f84ce9dd853f80e4171fc603b6a37","tid":252272,"uid":1786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"因管理不善而從全球最佳航空公司排名榜節節下跌的國泰航空"},{"pid":"2bf3a92894e63614fa8f0f1246843a09135b75ab","tid":252272,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"求教：劏豬凳點解"},{"pid":"558ebeb0018f8370211b6523eb3925d099f39ee1","tid":252272,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"聽日東方可以兩單<br />\ncx 裁員同呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034382a93563d665dea2d3cb164375a4b498eb4c","tid":252272,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求教：劏豬凳點解</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469b501118421618e9fd05e3252898674ee887c6